# Protein Packed Chickpea Pasta

Based on [https://saucestache.com/the-easiest-protein-packed-pasta-meal-prep-i-make/](https://saucestache.com/the-easiest-protein-packed-pasta-meal-prep-i-make) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251117222514/https://saucestache.com/the-easiest-protein-packed-pasta-meal-prep-i-make/))

